  "description": "This refrigerator does more than just freeze or refrigerate food. The model stores food in such a way as to make the shelf life of the food as long as possible. For this purpose, the refrigeration unit has received a number of innovative tools. With Multi Air Flow technology, the flow of cold begins to flow to each shelf and each drawer separately. The cooling system responds quickly to heat loss. Refrigerator LG GA-B509CQZM guarantees temperature maintenance with an accuracy of ±1 °C in the cooling zone and ±0.5 °C in the freezer. To make heat dissipation more efficient and faster, the cooling system additionally uses DoorCooling+ technology. With this function, the flow of cold air is directed directly to the door, which minimizes the heating of the workspace when the door leaf is open or from new products. This refrigerator differs from many analogs in low noise level. The volume of the compressor does not exceed 36 dB. The harmonicity of the body design is emphasized by the zero clearance option. The refrigerator can be placed in any corner, next to any furniture. If necessary, this model can be mounted even in a niche, as built-in units are installed.",
